metadata.name: Fuxia PlayBoy
metadata.description: This NFT celebrates the icon of sexiness, escape, lust and desire par excellence. It perfectly fits the artistâ€™s vision of the show business as perceived by the general public being linked to the sense of appearance and possession, as well as to the exploitation of the image and the ostentation of wealth.
